          <p class='first-para'>
            I thank the Minister for his comments. I do not intend to return to the discussion
            
            <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_101gc' title='Col. 101GC &mdash; HL Deb 10 June 2003 vol 649 c101GC' name='column_101gc' href='#column_101gc' rel='bookmark'>101GC</a>
            about devolution of powers to Wales, but this point also relates to a further amendment. This is a new policy and a new initiative. The point relates to wider publicity, if that is the right word&#x2014;if there has to be Treasury approval and so on. The accountability that we should like to see is not provided.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
